{
  "stem": "9878.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the farmer, oh, go, take the [INAUDIBLE] little girl too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My sister put on her kerchief, and she looked like a-- like a farmer's wife.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She jumped over the two children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She went to see my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At 5:00, the farmer-- wonderful gentleman, a Pollack, wanted to-- a Polish fellow-- he wanted to pick my-- my sister up, because he was promising he was going to take her back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They wouldn't let him in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Germans and Ukrainians, the army of German soldiers, army of Ukrainians, surrounded the whole area, and they wouldn't let nobody in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The next day, the selections started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the thing that I'm going to say about the ghetto, what has happened, is only because I read from it what people-- what survivors told, because I was not in the ghetto at this time.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was out by the farmer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the way they started systematically driving the Jew-- the people into the-- seven kilometers away in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Not direction that I was working, but in a north direction of the city towards Rovno.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There the name of the town-- little village is [INAUDIBLE], where the big grave site they dug.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the irony of this that the night before, Jewish workers, jewish laborers had to dig the graves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they dig the graves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were so bold, the Germans, to-- the Ukrainians watched them, and the Ukrainians made fun of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The graves, you dig good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Dig very good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "These are the graves for your wives and children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the Germans were so, so adamant to take-- to see if anybody has maybe have a five golden piece in pocket.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Maybe somebody put it-- a ring, like, my mother wouldn't give part of her ring.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
